property.name: note
property.value:
The rain intensity corresponds to the 'Rain' parameter where 1 is torrential rain and 0 is no rain.
The wind intensity corresponds to the 'Wind' parameter where 1 is blizzard level and 0 is no wind.
The lightning parameter is a discrete value, where 0 is no lightning and 1 is lightning - think of this as a trigger.
Event Type: 2D Location: 0/Managers/WeatherManager/WeatherManager.cs Triggered: On Start
